{"tid":2041247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我必須生一千次，我只願意生在那裡，我那小小多山的國家。","createTime":"2020-05-29T06:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T06:59:18.000Z","uid":136431,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c63d25a0af37b73ddb1711b5280be965cef78943","tid":2041247,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"‪台灣，鄭南榕：「如果我必須死一千次，我只願意死在那裡，‬如果我必須生一千次，我只願意生在那裡，我那小小多山的國家。」<br />\n<br />\n‪香港都係一個小小多山嘅國家。‬<br />\n如果有手足係想走想離開嘅，要知道係一時推卻，等候他日光復。同時間仲有人繼續喺度奮鬥，為嘅都係香港，我哋小小多山嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n民族自立，唔係一朝一夕，但起碼必先自強。<br />\n<br />\n做手頭上做到嘅嘢，哪怕只係嗰0.0000000001%，打個比喻，假設你係和理非，你都唔會諗到自己送上嘅一條索帶，就已經幫到手足換取時間；一把遮已經救到好多個手足；Twitter 嘅一個RT 就會促成國際戰線嘅成果。積少成多，終成巨浪，由自強到自由自立，冇人知要行幾耐，但起碼大家要肯行。<br />\n<br />\n無論你喺邊，做緊任何路線，你覺得有用做去做。香港民族，一切以自由為目標，以此目標為本。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Rebellion is built on Hope</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">民族自強</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ce5ba653cde168ace4e6953afc9e4bd58b0fe945","tid":2041247,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc7c506b5dc28329b11dc8ae7bd58516a560c2c","tid":2041247,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"講漏咗，就算要走，唔好忘記香港人嘅身份，仲有好多嘢可以做到。一直以嚟，我哋都好好彩仲有好多海外手足幫手，先可以行到今時今日。<br />\n<br />\n香港係要自己救，國際戰線亦係自救不可或缺嘅一部分。"},{"pid":"b28c53c0287119a9e62c8942e15e376dc635278b","tid":2041247,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b7e6df3d9fe1d0cdc9fd08a68a0ae48dbce8b6","tid":2041247,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果個個都走<br />\n五十年你肯定仲有香港人？"},{"pid":"cd7173a179db35dd41daf780390162710f9fa765","tid":2041247,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70b7e6df3d9fe1d0cdc9fd08a68a0ae48dbce8b6","tid":2041247,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果個個都走<br />\n五十年你肯定仲有香港人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"事在人為"},{"pid":"e0a4748a18248dce5e0708c3480f0736e48ac0f7","tid":2041247,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6681cba7b5bcf48d94025104b13bc268a3154586","tid":2041247,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"如果要走，我會等埋手足先走<br />\n<br />\n要走一齊走"},{"pid":"8887deeee2ed9f4948521b8958f7655b22eb47cf","tid":2041247,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Asgard is not a place, <br />\nit's a people.</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0bd2b58cfb4252da7f4123866f8e012fe4d747d","tid":2041247,"uid":337036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8887deeee2ed9f4948521b8958f7655b22eb47cf","tid":2041247,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Asgard is not a place, <br />\nit's a people.</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"比唔到正皮 但同意"}]}